<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>rby̱ wạlhy</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - rby̱ wạlhy wfạdyạ ḥbk mly̱ ạldnyạ ʿlyh
 ḍạmn mʿạk ạ̉yạm jạyh mlyạnh frḥ wkẖyr wslạm
 ḥty̱ lw ạlḍyqẗ sẖdydẗ ḥty̱ lw ạlfrḥẗ bʿydẗ kl wʿwdk ly jdydẗ
 ạfrḥwạ by kmạn wkmạn
 1- kl ạmạ bbʿd tndhly̱ wḥdk tʿyn ḍʿfy wjhly mḥtạj lạ̹ydk trfʿny̱
 dh ạ̉nt ạlhy wfạdyạ
 tbqy̱ ạ̉nt mdh ḥyạty qạdr tsd ạḥtyạjạty̱ ʿạrf bḍʿfy ạ̉nạ ạlkẖạṭy̱ʾ
 wlmạ ạgẖyb ạ̉nt tjyny̱
 2- wqt ạlḥrwb btkẖbyny̱ tẓhr fy̱ ḍʿfy̱ tqwyny̱ trfʿny̱ tmsk bymyny̱
 mn ḍyq lfrḥ tʿdyny̱
 wlạ mrh mmkn tnsạny ḥbk yʿyn ḍʿf ạymạny̱ mn gẖyrk ạ̉nt njạny
 wfy wqt ḥzny ywạsyny
 ạnt yạrb trs kẖlạṣy̱ srạj lrjly̱ wtạj rạsy̱ tnhḍny̱ lmạ bạkwn nạsy̱
 skh msẖyỷtk wkẖlạṣy̱</lyrics>
<author>mmdwḥ mykẖạỷyl, ṣfwt nạjy̱</author>
<hymn_number>5806</hymn_number>
</song>